snippet.title: Story of Seasons: Pioneers of Olive Town – Nintendo Direct Mini: Partner Showcase | October 2020
snippet.description:
Leave the city behind and cultivate your farm from the ground up in a brand-new STORY OF SEASONS game! Your new farm life awaits when STORY OF SEASONS: Pioneers of Olive Town crops up on Nintendo Switch on March 23, 2021.

#StoryofSeasons #NintendoSwitch
